ted_topic_webapp_v2/
├── TEDLIUM_r1              # Datasets
│   └── stm/               
│   └── README          
├── final_v2.ipynb          # Basic dashboard implemented, including Topic classification, Keywords Extraction and Evolution tracking
├── __pycache__             # Python bytecode cache (auto-generated)
├── audio_upload/           # Temporary directory for user-uploaded audio files 
├── static
│   └── stm/                # Original TED .stm transcript files
│   └── style.css           # Optional CSS file (currently unused in templates)  
├── templates
│   └── index.html          # Home page (Flask template, includes Dash dashboard + audio upload)
│   └── result.html         # Recommendation result display page (Flask template)
├── app.py 
├── dashboard_test.py       # Unused
├── dashboard.py            # Main Dash application (topic trend, word cloud, sample STM preview)
├── README
├── requirements.txt        # Required Python dependencies
├── run.py                  # Main program, Dash web app entry point
├── stm_topic.csv           # Precomputed TED topic classification and keywords (from topic modeling)
└── utils.py                # Utility functions for transcription (Whisper) and topic recommendation


1. pip install -r requirements.txt
2. python3 'run.py'
